{
  "texts": [
    "The results demonstrate that the method achieves excellent performance in TREx and zsRE datasets and exhibits remarkable robustness in TACRED dataset.",
    "The process of text-to-image generation is a challenging one, requiring a model to demonstrate a high degree of natural language understanding and to convey this understanding through an image, in contrast to the typical format of textual data.",
    "In a pioneering study, Li et al. (2022a) proposed the use of retrieval techniques to enhance the quality of text-to-image generation.",
    "They conducted a comparative analysis of the quality and quantity of the generated images with mainstream models on the CUB and COCO datasets.",
    "Their findings demonstrated that all models outperformed their contemporaries."
  ]
}